name: Larry Hogan
tweet: Maryland is the first state in the nation to pass bipartisan legislation to suspend the gas tax. name: Larry Hogan
tweet: Yesterday, I signed into law an immediate suspension of the gas tax - the first state in the nation to do so.   Though it is not a cure-all, this action will provide some relief at the pump.
